<br />\n病人昨日轉送至普通病房，今日轉送瑪嘉烈醫院隔離病房繼續接受治療，現時情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n中心調查顯示，男童潛伏期內曾到訪外祖父母深圳家，其家居有散養家禽，但病人最近沒有直接接觸禽鳥，亦沒有進食未經煮熟的家禽或接觸病人，家居接觸者至今沒有出現病徵。<br />\n#立場"},{"pid":"f4ccf538ecc0ee102c29bd5ef011b61a891b4078","tid":1868150,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8b60691ab9f48162675cbff244d4cea79acc4782","tid":1868150,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a36889f2d5b81eced279fc35e3a365757d138784","tid":1868150,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3185f61ec144a7b4d52503e032e258dd415c38a1","tid":1868150,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:37:09.000Z","msg":"搵麻x解決"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/43b793fe16b801fabaad41cb56916d14/tumblr_ovbvcean5H1rla1lvo1_500.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F43b793fe16b801fabaad41cb56916d14%2Ftumblr_ovbvcean5H1rla1lvo1_500.gifv&h=ec69f200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻x<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:40:05.000Z","msg":"qq"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"gg"},{"pid":"0c3eecd227446c656ab6780e18f885e1ae221cf0","tid":1868150,"uid":109416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7563a7b58cb3d2d8eea912abf78981c4c6644039","tid":1868150,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:01:59.000Z","msg":"輸港女女只會越來越少，有又驚肺然，咁唯有學秋生咁自我解決啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4aBPZu2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4aBPZu2.gif&h=2a7fcdb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"飛機杯會唔會比較好。"},{"pid":"ff8f12006cd45772fa918b5af717a0583e744204","tid":1868150,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c3eecd227446c656ab6780e18f885e1ae221cf0"